======
README
======

Author: Andy Todd
Name: Mainly Green (version 2), updated by Akai for Pyblosxom 1.5.2+

Installation
============

1. Place the ``html.flav`` directory in the ``flavourdir`` specified in your 
   ``config.py`` file.

2. Copy the ``halfcooked.css`` file to a directory that is served by your
   webserver.

3. Edit ``head.html`` and change the ``href`` attribute value in the line::

    <link rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" href="/styles/halfcooked.css" />

   to the url that the ``halfcooked.css`` file will be served from.



